com.sponsorpay.publisher.interstitial

Interface SPInterstitialAdListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SPInterstitialActivity

    public interface SPInterstitialAdListener

    Interface that defines the methods to be implemented in order to get notifications about the status of an ad.

    Used internally by the SPInterstitialActivity in order to return the proper status when finished.
